                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" id="">Where will your funds go?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body" style="overflow:hidden">
                    The funds you donate to this emergency appeal will support emergency response for displaced children and families in Ukraine and neighbouring countries. World Vision will use donations in Ukraine through partners when it is possible. If these funds are not needed due to the peaceful resolution of the situation in Ukraine, they will be used to help displaced and refugee populations elsewhere in the Middle East and Eastern European region. Should we receive contributions more than the needs in a particular emergency appeal, we will use the excess in other emergency-related activity.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
